{"text": "Subject: Your pipeline data is lying to you\n\nHi {{first_name}},\n\nMost RevOps teams we talk to discover their CRM data is 40% stale within 90 days of entry.\n\nThat's not a process problem. It's a tooling problem.\n\nWe built [Product] to fix it. Book 15 minutes this week and we'll show you exactly where your pipeline data breaks down.\n\n[Book a call →]", "channel": "email", "campaign": "outbound_q1", "brief": "Cold outbound email to RevOps leaders", "approved_at": "2025-02-03"}
{"text": "The average B2B sales cycle is 3 months longer than it was 5 years ago. Buyers are more cautious. Committees are bigger. Approval chains are longer.\n\nThe teams winning deals in this market have one thing in common: they show, they don't tell.\n\nWhat does your demo look like? We can help.\n\n#B2BSales #SalesEnablement", "channel": "linkedin", "campaign": "thought_leadership", "brief": "Thought leadership post on B2B sales cycle", "approved_at": "2025-02-20"}
